
Template: networkoptix-mediaserver/ecs_host
Type: string
Default: localhost
Description: Enterprise Controller host:

Template: networkoptix-mediaserver/ecs_port
Type: string
Default: 7001
Description: Enterprise Controller port:

Template: networkoptix-mediaserver/ecs_login
Type: string
Default: admin
Description: Enterprise Controller login:

Template: networkoptix-mediaserver/ecs_password
Type: string
Default: 
Description: Enterprise Controller password:
 If empty the old password (if exists) will be used.

Template: networkoptix-mediaserver/storage
Type: string
Default: /opt/networkoptix/mediaserver/var/data
Description: Storage folder

Template: networkoptix-mediaserver/ecs_port_invalid
Type: error
Description: The port is invalid. Please try again.

Template: networkoptix-mediaserver/storage_abspath
Type: error
Description: Please specify an absolute path (starting with /)

Template: networkoptix-mediaserver/storage_cant_create
Type: error
Description: Can't create directory. Please check it's correct
 and you have appropriate permissions.
